dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Florence County, WI YE2016
dc_description_s: These polygon and line data layers represent hydrography for Florence County, Wisconsin in year end 2016. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Florence_Hydro_YE2016. The features included in this geodatabase are 'FLORENCE_HYDRO_2016_LINE' and 'FLORENCE_HYDRO_2016_POLY'.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
